title: Dinosauria - Part IV: Nuevogato
description: After the events of Dinosauria - Part A Memory of Time...Jack Pennywise has discovered his true destiny, and it's not what he had been told it would be. In fact, it's the complete opposite, and he's determined not to let it come true. But a chain of events, starting with a daring rescue attempt, may be Jack's first steps toward his dark future...
author: J. Rock
